  "subject": "[COMMON] Add Label \"app\" to allow filtering in Istio",
  "commit_message": "[COMMON] Add Label \"app\" to allow filtering in Istio\n\nFor using \"matchLabels\" in istio the label \"app\" need to be\ndefined, which is missing in the common template.\nThis is needed e.g. in MariaDB SM compatibility\n\nIssue-ID: OOM-2820\n\nSigned-off-by: Andreas Geissler <andreas-geissler@telekom.de>\nChange-Id: I537ba3a6ff9c14fd43e14536eb89b4716bdb4a86\n",
